Assuming we have the pylintrc file from the Python style guide from TensorFlow
https://google.github.io/styleguide/pylintrc, and the pylint-ignore.md file
generated for mlt/master with 5c67495c06eb797ac156197e5d31c1c5ff08ca2b, the
steps for running pylint-ignore locally (in a conda/python environment):
1. pip install pylint pylint-ignore
2. pylint-ignore --rcfile=./pylintrc ./python